 <div class="postConteudo"><table border="0" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2" width="400" align="center">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Pedro Martinelli<br />
<img src="http://veja.abril.com.br/080709/imagens/artigo1.jpg" border="0" alt="" vspace="1" width="400" height="263" /></td>
